BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kFjHPgpIwmdp7lmzBHrKk
SUMMARY:Wife of Headless Man Investigates Her Own Disappearance
DTSTAMP:20260327T045205Z
DTSTART:20260407T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Written by Yussef El Guindi\n\nDirected by Lucien Oberleitner\n
	\nA reporter experiences a chunk of missing time after interviewing a tech
	 billionaire who hasn’t taken kindly to her negative articles about him. W
	as she drugged during the meal? How did she end up in a hotel room after m
	eeting him in a restaurant? And if she was drugged\, is that why\, when sh
	e returns home\, her husband appears as fully alive and functioning and he
	adless?\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wife-of-headless-
	man-investigates-her-own-disappearance/18216693/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAt
	oday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wife-of-headless-man-inve
	stigates-her-own-disappearance/18216693/2026-04-06T00
LOCATION:Annex Theatre\, 1100 E Pike St\, Seattle\, WA
