BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TMSoA2BtWxdRUk4Lt8-Bx
SUMMARY:Jonah Marks (Album Release: POEMS) w/Special Guests
DTSTAMP:20260327T045206Z
DTSTART:20260516T033000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $15 ($20.09 after fees)\n\nDay of: $20 ($26.27 after f
	ees)\n\nJonah Marks:\n\nJonah Marks is an independent singer-songwriter an
	d rapper crafting soulful\, story-driven lyrics through Hip Hop and R&B. A
	fter spending more than a decade working behind the scenes in artist manag
	ement and concert production\, Jonah Marks steps fully into his own creati
	ve voice on POEMS\, a 10-song narrative that challenges modern disconnecti
	on and overreliance on technology. The album opens with “Poems Over Cell P
	hones\,” a thesis-driven track that sets the tone for a journey away from 
	constant digital output and toward presence and creativity. As the record 
	unfolds\, its production becomes increasingly organic and acoustic\, culmi
	nating in the community-focused closing track\, “People Over Poems.” POEMS
	 is primarily produced by Elan Wright\, with additional production from He
	avywait\, Noah Coinflip\, and Damono. The album features rich live instrum
	entation\, including piano\, strings\, percussion\, choir vocals\, and a g
	uest feature from hip-hop artist Rell Be Free.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset
	 Tavern is a strictly 21+ bar and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s 
	for entry.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/t707c6381cac\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/t707c6381cac
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
