	U WAKU makes its Seattle debut on Saturday\, May 30th\, 2026DJ Jak Syn wil
	l be throwing down a steady supply of Anime-adjacent jams. Expect to find 
	yourself dancing to a mix of kawaii bass\, nightcore\, synthwave\, future 
	funk\, chiptune\, EDM remixes & more.Cosplay Highly Encouraged!!!Cosplayer
	s\, anime fans\, and nightlifers alike\, join us in a space where expressi
	ve outfits\, character-inspired looks\, and shared fandom take center stag
	e\, whether youre serving main-character energy\, chaotic sidekick vibes\,
